sql_query.sql: SET client_min_messages TO 'warning'
SET standard_conforming_strings = on
SET intervalstyle = iso_8601

SELECT t.oid, t.typname
FROM pg_type as t
WHERE t.typname IN ('int2', 'int4', 'int8', 'oid', 'float4', 'float8', 'numeric', 'bool', 'timestamp', 'timestamptz')
SET SESSION timezone TO 'UTC'

SELECT t.oid, t.typname, t.typelem, t.typdelim, t.typinput, r.rngsubtype, t.typtype, t.typbasetype
FROM pg_type as t
LEFT JOIN pg_range as r ON oid = rngtypid
WHERE
  t.typname IN ('int2', 'int4', 'int8', 'oid', 'float4', 'float8', 'text', 'varchar', 'char', 'name', 'bpchar', 'bool', 'bit', 'varbit', 'date', 'money', 'bytea', 'point', 'hstore', 'json', 'jsonb', 'cidr', 'inet', 'uuid', 'xml', 'tsvector', 'macaddr', 'citext', 'ltree', 'line', 'lseg', 'box', 'path', 'polygon', 'circle', 'numeric', 'interval', 'time', 'timestamp', 'timestamptz')

SELECT t.oid, t.typname, t.typelem, t.typdelim, t.typinput, r.rngsubtype, t.typtype, t.typbasetype
FROM pg_type as t
LEFT JOIN pg_range as r ON oid = rngtypid
WHERE
  t.typtype IN ('r', 'e', 'd')
SELECT c.relname FROM pg_class c LEFT JOIN pg_namespace n ON n.oid = c.relnamespace WHERE n.nspname = ANY (current_schemas(false)) AND c.relname = 'schema_migrations' AND c.relkind IN ('r','p')
SELECT c.relname FROM pg_class c LEFT JOIN pg_namespace n ON n.oid = c.relnamespace WHERE n.nspname = ANY (current_schemas(false)) AND c.relname = 'ar_internal_metadata' AND c.relkind IN ('r','p')
SELECT "schema_migrations"."version" FROM "schema_migrations" ORDER BY "schema_migrations"."version" ASC
SELECT c.relname FROM pg_class c LEFT JOIN pg_namespace n ON n.oid = c.relnamespace WHERE n.nspname = ANY (current_schemas(false)) AND c.relkind IN ('r','v','m','p','f')

SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),
       pg_get_expr(d.adbin, d.adrelid), a.attnotnull, a.atttypid, a.atttypmod,
       c.collname, col_description(a.attrelid, a.attnum) AS comment,
       a.attidentity AS identity,
       attgenerated as attgenerated
  FROM pg_attribute a
  LEFT JOIN pg_attrdef d ON a.attrelid = d.adrelid AND a.attnum = d.adnum
  LEFT JOIN pg_type t ON a.atttypid = t.oid
  LEFT JOIN pg_collation c ON a.attcollation = c.oid AND a.attcollation <> t.typcollation
 WHERE a.attrelid = '"ip_blocks"'::regclass
   AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
 ORDER BY a.attnum
SHOW max_identifier_length
SHOW search_path
SELECT "ip_blocks"."ip" FROM "ip_blocks" WHERE "ip_blocks"."severity" = $1

  LEFT JOIN pg_type t ON a.atttypid = t.oid
  LEFT JOIN pg_collation c ON a.attcollation = c.oid AND a.attcollation <> t.typcollation
 WHERE a.attrelid = '"site_uploads"'::regclass
   AND a.attnum > 0 AND NOT a.attisdropped
 ORDER BY a.attnum
SELECT "site_uploads".* FROM "site_uploads" WHERE "site_uploads"."var" = $1 LIMIT $2

SELECT a.attname, format_type(a.atttypid, a.atttypmod),

       c.collname, col_description(a.attrelid, a.attnum) AS comment,
       a.attidentity AS identity,
       attgenerated as attgenerated
  FROM pg_attribute a

 ORDER BY a.attnum

sql_query.sql:
SELECT a.attname
  FROM (
         SELECT indrelid, indkey, generate_subscripts(indkey, 1) idx
           FROM pg_index
          WHERE indrelid = '"settings"'::regclass
            AND indisprimary
       ) i
  JOIN pg_attribute a
    ON a.attrelid = i.indrelid
   AND a.attnum = i.indkey[i.idx]
 ORDER BY i.idx
